rComments: Sana Keita is the best first year prof there is for calc and linear algebra. Go to his classes and pay attention you will pass with flying colours!
Really good professor ! Just take him if you have the chance to.

Sana Keita was an amazing prof! I had him in both MAT1700 and MAT 1702, he lets u know what is on the exams and provides practice ones that are very similar. He is very nice and will always respond to your emails outside of class. I would highly recommend him!

rComments: Find some practice Exams online and you will do very well! He is a great teacher!

Les notes de cours sont extrêment bien organisées et le prof couvre ce qui est dans les notes de cours. Ces évualitions très rapprochées permettent de comprendre la matière de manière très digeste et d'avoir de bonnes notes bien que la correction soit dure lors des examens.

Very very thorough notes provided online. Lectures don't have much that isn't in the notes so I often skipped them. He covers exactly everything needed for tests - no more, no less, which prepares you well but also the class wasn't very interesting because it just provided the necessary formulas/etc without any additional explanation.
Great

Prof Keita is well organized, lecture notes are clear and given ahead of time. Math department is pretty standardized (at least for the big first year courses) so he prepares you well for the exams. Textbook questions are given in the syllabus; it's not necessary but you need to buy a license for homework. Overall, he is a nice and caring prof!
He is very organized making his class easy to follow and study for. His tests reflect the material covered in class. He cares about his students and wants you to succeed. Take him if you can.
Very good notes and really seems to care about his students
He gives a lot of homework. Mr. Keita cares about his students' grades and he is always kind. To add, his exams are not the easiest but you need to study hard.
He is alright

Un trop bon profr qui est très ouvert aux suggestions de ses étudiants. Les examens sont également faciles, pour autant que vous vous assuriez de faire vous-même chaque devoir dans Mobius et de le comprendre !
Hard to understand at times, tests and exams don't reflect the material well enough; the evaluations are always harder. Avoid
Great prof who cares about his students and his midterms are very easy if you do the homeworks.
Just great

Prof Keita didn't seem like he wanted to be teaching whenever he taught our class. The content isn't too hard, but I had to do a lot of self-teaching with this prof.

Les notes de cours sont extrêmement claires. Les examens ressemblent exactement aux devoirs. Lisez les notes de cours et refaites les devoirs vous allez passer ce cours facilement. Excellent prof. No word to describe him

Prof Keita is a decent prof. His course notes are super-well organized which is insanely useful for late-minute cramming before a midterm, but his online lectures are confusing at best. Calculus II is a hard math course I'd recommend relying on external resources to grasp the material. Also, make use of office hours !
Mr. Keita est un bon prof. Il explique clairement la matière même si le cours est en ligne. J'aimerai l'avoir en présentiel. Nhésites pas a prendre un cours avec lui

The best university prof I have had so far, by a landslide. Feels like a real classroom even when the course was taken online. The prof has incredible explanations and is very caring towards his students. Would definitely recommend.
Super! Explique clairement et insiste sur les notions qu'on doit bien comprendre pour assimiler le cours! Je vous le recommande.
